I"0<p>We are pleased to announce the release for <a href="https://opendistro.github.io/for-elasticsearch/downloads.html">Open Distro for Elasticsearch 1.9.0</a> that introduces <a href="https://github.com/opendistro-for-elasticsearch/performance-analyzer-rca">Root Cause Analysis Engine in Performance Analyzer</a>, batch actions like <a href="https://github.com/opendistro-for-elasticsearch/anomaly-detection-kibana-plugin/pull/195">start, stop</a> and <a href="https://github.com/opendistro-for-elasticsearch/anomaly-detection-kibana-plugin/pull/204">delete</a> for anomaly detectors in Anomaly Detection, <a href="https://github.com/opendistro-for-elasticsearch/anomaly-detection-kibana-plugin/pull/244">support for remote cluster indexes</a> in Anomaly Detection, and an ability to <a href="https://github.com/opendistro-for-elasticsearch/index-management/pull/241">set index priority action</a> in Index State Management feature. Open Distro for Elasticsearch 1.9.0 can be downloaded <a href="https://opendistro.github.io/for-elasticsearch/downloads.html">here</a>.</p>
